### CREATE tag (requires auth)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/tags
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "names": {
    "EN": "New Tag",
    "ZH": "新标签"
  },
  "slug": "new-tag"
}

### UPDATE tag (requires auth)
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/tags/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "names": {
    "EN": "Updated Tag",
    "ZH": "更新的标签"
  },
  "slug": "updated-tag"
}

### DELETE tag (requires auth)
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/tags/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}